{
  "stem": "25651.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was one thing that impressed me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It looks a little like Rodin's Rodin probably took the idea from Michelangelo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Perhaps or perhaps not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the other-- and the other one was the Laocoon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the Laocoon sort of took my fancy because of the story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's a Greek man with his sons who is fighting serpents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there are serpents-- it's a statue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't think it's Michelangelo, but it's that sort of period.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I forget who it's by, but it's a famous statue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it's in the-- it's in the Vatican.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And again in adult life, I went to see that statue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it's a story of this man being punished by Hera, who sends the snakes to kill him and his sons.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they fight these serpents, you see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So this caught my imagination.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What a terrible death it must be to, to be, to be asphyxiated by serpents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I mean, you know, whilst this is a horror story, a child doesn't see it like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You just sort of-- it's a story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It's a, it's, it's-- I think I had an interest in history ever since that sort of, that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we went to cheder, and it was quite ineffectual because the teachers were inadequate, and it was reform, and it was-- the only thing that's interesting is that when I was learning Hebrew after the war, in 1948 in Israel, I still remember the pronunciation, which is this German reform, you see, like the vav with a dot is 'ow' instead of 'oh,' which it is both in Ashkenazi and in Sephardi Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 74
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there are all kinds of differences in pronunciation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I do genealogy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was looking up somebody called Horowitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
